            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>转扩！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#怎么判断是否感染肺炎支原体#</span></a>】肺炎支原体，主要通过飞沫传播，儿童是易感人群，青少年、大人也可能中招！但<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#感染肺炎支原体不等于得了肺炎#</span></a>，它会出现咳嗽剧烈、干咳少痰，胸片显示网状结节状阴影或斑片状实变，与病毒感染和细菌感染完全不同。感染肺炎支原体后该怎么用药？戳👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4959062891364381" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hj25o2pyf3j60sk122k4k02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/DzTMTxtvlx089wZKF1OM01041200yXhV0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x